{"title":"Cane Creek Adds Purple Permanently to the Chroma Studio Collection","link":"https://bikerumor.com/cane-creek-adds-purple-permanently-to-the-chroma-studio-collection/","date":1740585665000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Purple-2048_edited_1-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Cane Creek Purple chroma studio\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-ultraviolet-purple-bike-parts/\" target=\"_blank\">Purple is popular again</a>. But did it ever <em>really</em> go out of style? That can be debated, but now purple has a new permanent home for the Cane Creek Chroma Studio Collection.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Chroma Studio is the name for Cane Creek’s collection of anodized parts which includes Hellbender headsets and bottom brackets, Helm mkII forks, and other small accessories like computer mounts. According to Cane Creek, purple has been the most popular color request since they launched the Chroma Studio in 2023. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-1536x1025.webp\" alt=\"Cane Creek Purple chroma studio hellbender 70 lite\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cane_Creek_Purple_Chroma_Burke_Lawrence_Photo_2k_19_of_56_9fcea1e7-a36e-43e3-ae11-dde8a98dafde.jpg-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with the addition of purple, Cane Creek is also including the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/cane-creek-hellbender-70-lite-and-slam-headsets-ltd-el-verde-eebrakes/\" target=\"_blank\">Hellbender 70 LITE headset</a> in the Chroma Studio color options. These headsets feature a hybrid aluminum bearing that drops 30% of the weight of a traditional steel bearing with minimized bearing balls and races. When combined with the lightweight preload assembly, the headset offers a 33% weight reduction over the standard Hellbender 70 headset. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T085125.204.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T085125.204.webp\" alt=\"Cane Creek Purple chroma studio\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T085125.204.webp 1080w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T085125.204-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T085125.204-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T085125.204-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T084611.446_8f5aad40-1f2d-43f2-9a3c-72447c2f7a5f.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T084611.446_8f5aad40-1f2d-43f2-9a3c-72447c2f7a5f.webp\" alt=\"cane creek purple computer mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T084611.446_8f5aad40-1f2d-43f2-9a3c-72447c2f7a5f.webp 1080w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T084611.446_8f5aad40-1f2d-43f2-9a3c-72447c2f7a5f-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T084611.446_8f5aad40-1f2d-43f2-9a3c-72447c2f7a5f-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Untitled_design_-_2025-02-25T084611.446_8f5aad40-1f2d-43f2-9a3c-72447c2f7a5f-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Now Available in Purple:  </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Helm MKII fork, Air, 29 (140mm, 150mm, 160mm)  </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hellbender 70 headset (4 configurations)  </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hellbender 70 LITE headset (3 configurations) <strong>NEW Chroma Studio Addition </strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Standard headset top cap </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Interlok Spacers</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hellbender 70 Bottom Bracket (BSA only)  </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Crank Preloader</li>\n\n\n\n<li>eeBarkeep  </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Computer Mount   </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.canecreek.com/collections/chroma-studio\" target=\"_blank\">canecreek.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/cane-creek-adds-purple-permanently-to-the-chroma-studio-collection/\">Cane Creek Adds Purple Permanently to the Chroma Studio Collection</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"8916302012d925e4487af4dbd4538a6c7b377368d1ff6d48c2797b0ed9477ad1","category":"Cycling"}